Use psql < create_scom.sql to :
 - create a scom database
 - create a scomuser user (password scompass)
 - create the tables in the scom database, including creating schema version info

Use psql < remove_scom.sql to :
 - remove scomuser privs on scom db
 - remove the scom db
 - remove the scomuser user

Restart GroundWork after doing either of these things.
